data.description: Are you in search of a single-level home with a seamless layout, abundant space, and convenient access to freeways and schools in the valley? Look no further - this immaculate home is precisely what you've been seeking. Enjoy the expansive living room, a spacious eat-in kitchen with ample cabinet and storage space, and extensive countertop areas. The generously sized bedrooms offer versatile arrangement possibilities. The backyard has an area designed for a hot tub, features a fenced area perfect for pets, and provides access to a large two-car garage with additional shelving for storage. The extended driveway easily accommodates an RV or multiple cars. Conveniently located near an elementary school, downtown shopping, and the 512 freeway
